<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">三　長老之譬喻二</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十七　須波離奢利耶</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七〇　槃奢古利耶（五指印）</cb:mulu><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.186" type="PTS_hide"></ref><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="18"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0263a" n="0263a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十八　拘物頭品</cb:mulu><head>第十八　拘物頭品</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七一　拘物頭瑪利耶（白蓮之華鬘）</cb:mulu><head>一七一　拘物頭瑪利耶（白蓮之華鬘）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0263a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0263a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>雪山深谷中，有大自然湖，吾生為羅剎，怖形持大力。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0263a0701">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0263a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>拘物頭花開，花大如車輪，爾時手折花，拆破其所集。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0263a0801"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.187"></ref>三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0263a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>兩足尊王者，阿塔他西佛，見花被揉潰，來至吾眼邊。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0263a0901">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0263a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>天中天佛陀，正覺尊駕臨，吾手捧花束，供獻彼佛陀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0263a1001">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0263a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>只要雪山在，不問居何處，具備盛花蓋，如來自往彼<note n="0263001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">訂正為 agamāsi（依暹羅本）。</note>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0263a1101">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0263a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>由捧此花供，十八劫之間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0263a1201">七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0263a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>十五劫往昔，統主有七人，其名稱千車<note n="0263002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sahassaratha（千車）。</note>，大力轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0263a1301">八</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0263a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0263a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0263a1401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者拘物頭瑪利耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0264a" n="0264a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七二　尼闍尼達耶迦（梯布施）</cb:mulu><head>一七二　尼闍尼達耶迦（梯布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0264a0701">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0264a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世間居上首，佛名憍陳如<note n="0264001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">過去二十四佛之第二佛。參閱 Jātaka, I, P. 30。</note>，吾為造登梯，彼登殿堂上。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0264a0801">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0264a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾心清淨故，享樂幾多福，等覺者之教，吾保最後身。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0264a0901">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0264a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>從今三萬劫，一千劫往昔，三人轉輪王，巴哈山報羅。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0264a1001">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0264a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0264a1101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者尼闍尼達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0264a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0265a" n="0265a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七三　拉提普庇耶（拉提花）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.188"></ref>一七三　拉提普庇耶（拉提花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0265a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0265a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>於此森林中，吾昔為獵夫，吾見毘婆尸，天中天之佛。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0265a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0265a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>忽見拉提花<note n="0265001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">ratti, rattika 樹名，其次之 kuṭaja dharaṇīruha 皆為植物名。</note>，庫達等花開，吾採花與根，獻與彼大仙。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0265a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0265a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>依捧獻花故，九十一劫間，吾不知惡趣，施花此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0265a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0265a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第八劫往昔，名喚善淨信<note n="0265002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 Suppasannasanāmako（善淨信）。</note>，大力具七寶，其出而為王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0265a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0265a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0265a0801" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者拉提普庇耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0265a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0266a" n="0266a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七四　烏達巴那達耶迦（水井布施）</cb:mulu><head>一七四　烏達巴那達耶迦（水井布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0266a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>毘婆尸佛陀，吾為作水井，向佛施供食，爾時並勸說。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0266a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>時作此善業，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，水井施果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0266a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a0601" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者烏達巴那達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七五　西哈薩那達耶迦（獅子座布施）</cb:mulu><head>一七五　西哈薩那達耶迦（獅子座布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a0901">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0266a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>巴多穆塔拉，世主將涅槃，吾心清淨喜，布施獅子座。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a1001">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0266a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>以多香華鬘，齎福來此世<note n="0266001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 sukhāvaho（異本）。</note>，於彼施供養，眾人多入滅。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a1101"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.189"></ref>三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0266a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾心清淨喜，禮拜菩提樹，十萬劫之間，吾不墮惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a1201">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0266a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>一萬五千劫，其名喚積戒<note n="0266002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sīluccaya（積戒）。</note>，彼等有八人，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a1301">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0266a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0266a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0266a1401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者西哈薩那達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0267a" n="0267a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七六　瑪格達提迦（道布施）</cb:mulu><head>一七六　瑪格達提迦（道布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0267a0701">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0267a0701" style="margin-left:3em"><l>兩足人中尊，阿諾瑪達西，齎福來此世，步行水滿處。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0267a0801">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0267a0801" style="margin-left:3em"><l>舉足幾花跡，頭上耀光輝，清淨吾心喜，禮拜撒散花。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0267a0901">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0267a0901" style="margin-left:3em"><l>二萬劫往昔，其名謂花蓋<note n="0267001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Pupphachadaniya（花蓋）。</note>，五人有大力，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0267a1001">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0267a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0267a1101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者瑪格達提迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0267a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0268a" n="0268a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七七　耶迦提毘耶（一燈）</cb:mulu><head>一七七　耶迦提毘耶（一燈）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0268a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0268a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>巴多穆塔拉，無上菩提樹，清淨吾心喜，燈火施一座。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0268a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0268a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>不論生何處，只要有積福，惡趣吾不知施燈此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0268a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0268a0501" style="margin-left:3em"><l>一萬六千劫，其名稱月光<note n="0268001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Candābha（月光）。</note>，四人有大力，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0268a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0268a0601" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0268a0701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者耶迦第毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0268a1101" style="margin-left:22em">——第九誦品——</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七八　瑪尼普奢伽（摩尼供養）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.190"></ref>一七八　瑪尼普奢伽（摩尼供養）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0268a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0268a1401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0268a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>雪山之麓下，河水有源發，彼處多水源<note n="0268001-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">訂正為 Cānūpa-（暹羅本）。</note>，自存者所居。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0269a" n="0269a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0269a0101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0269a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>佳景心氣爽，持造摩尼椅，清淨吾心喜，獻施予佛陀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0269a0201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0269a0201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>依施摩尼故，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0269a0301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0269a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>十二劫往昔，其名稱百光<note n="0269002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sataraṁsi（百光）。</note>，大力有八人，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0269a0401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0269a0401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0269a0501" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者瑪尼普奢伽長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七九　提乞奢迦（三困苦）</cb:mulu><head>一七九　提乞奢迦（三困苦）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0269a1201">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0269a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>盤頭摩帝市，吾時為良醫，諸人陷苦病，齎福予多眾。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0269a1301">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0269a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>明知展戒具，猶見沙門病，清淨心內喜，當時吾施藥。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0269a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0269a1401">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0269a1401" style="margin-left:3em"><l>沙門制諸根，彼病得痊癒，毘婆尸侍者，其名稱無憂。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0270a" n="0270a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0270a0101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0270a0101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>施與醫藥故，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，施藥此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0270a0201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0270a0201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第八劫往昔，名謂一切藥<note n="0270001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sabbosadha（一切藥）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0270a0301">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0270a0301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0270a0401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者提乞奢迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八〇　山古泊達伽（近侍僧團）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.191"></ref>一八〇　山古泊達伽（近侍僧團）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0270a1001">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0270a1001" style="margin-left:3em"><l>毘舍浮佛前，吾為僧苑僕，清淨心內喜，事無上僧團。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0270a1101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0270a1101" style="margin-left:3em"><l>爾時積業故，二十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，近侍此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0270a1201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0270a1201" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第七劫往昔，七人名展被<note n="0270001-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Samotthaṭa（展被）。</note>，大力具七寶，有為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0270a1301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0270a1301" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0270a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0270a1401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者山古泊達伽長老宣唱此等劫。</p>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0271a" n="0271a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0271a0401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">攝頌：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a05"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgN29p0271a0501" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:3em">拘物頭與尼闍尼、拉提普與烏達巴、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a06"/><l style="text-indent:3em">西哈薩與瑪格達、耶迦提庇、瑪尼普、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a07"/><l style="text-indent:3em">提乞奢迦、古帕達、十人共偈四十九。</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>